title: Daily mission event?
body:
Is this Daily mission event over? 
Im not getting any new missions and havent gotten new ones for around 2 weeks. 
maybe more than 2 weeks, might not have noticed it earlier but atleast 2 weeks.

replies.body: You're talking about the [**Versus Event**](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/events/vs-2017)? Yea that ended back on 6/29. There are currently 2 missions for Kayn, but you'll only have access to them if you own him. Once he goes free to play everyone will get the missions.
